1003
01:46:53,899 --> 01:46:55,060
[SPEAKER_19] Thank you.

1004
01:46:55,060 --> 01:46:57,659
[SPEAKER_19] Sanja Tomidzic from the Croatia National Bank.

1005
01:46:57,659 --> 01:47:03,239
[SPEAKER_19] Well, actually, I'm also going to address the question to Ms. Whitlocks, unfortunately.

1006
01:47:03,239 --> 01:47:12,699
[SPEAKER_19] Not the other panelists, but all the panelists today are talking about the digital euro project and having in mind and talking about the retail digital euro.

1007
01:47:13,180 --> 01:47:23,960
[SPEAKER_19] And I can, let's say, completely understand the narrative behind the digital euro and especially coming from the international and European relations area.

1008
01:47:25,399 --> 01:47:34,720
[SPEAKER_19] Within this time of the rising geopolitical fragmentation, the strategic autonomy argument seems to me very appealing.

1009
01:47:34,720 --> 01:47:43,439
[SPEAKER_19] And, you know, to have a solution that will work, even if the other solutions or infrastructure spill, is very important.

1010
01:47:43,439 --> 01:47:49,500
[SPEAKER_19] So I definitely can subscribe to this way of payment.

1011
01:47:49,500 --> 01:48:01,079
[SPEAKER_19] But on the other hand, I think that in a steady state, let's say, situation, the wholesale digital euro might be even more important.

1012
01:48:01,220 --> 01:48:14,220
[SPEAKER_19] And especially since it can also boost some other European European Union projects, like the Capital Markets Union, for instance, and not to mention that it could also strengthen the international role of the euro.

1013
01:48:14,220 --> 01:48:21,840
[SPEAKER_19] So can you maybe also tell us something about how we stand with the wholesale digital euro project?

1014
01:48:23,220 --> 01:48:35,380
[SPEAKER_18] Well, what we say, we already have a digital wholesale, the CBDC, I mean, it's target, everything is, there's nothing tangible, there's no cash there, I mean.

1015
01:48:35,380 --> 01:48:44,119
[SPEAKER_18] So in our view on wholesale, we already have a digital wholesale, central bank digital currency.

1016
01:48:44,119 --> 01:48:55,000
